v11

## Changes

* Adds support for Nix 2.6.1

* Changes default Nix version from 2.6.0 to 2.6.1

* Adds support for setting up `/nix` on a `tmpfs` mount.
  See https://github.com/nixbuild/nix-quick-install-action/blob/v11/action.yml#L26.

## Known issues

* `macos-latest` not currently not supported, use `macos-10.15` instead.
  See https://github.com/nixbuild/nix-quick-install-action/issues/7
